Class ApplicantRepo

Object
ApplicantRepo
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepo, IUserRepo<Applicant>
public class ApplicantRepo extends Object implements IUserRepo<Applicant>
Repository class that manages all Applicant objects. Provides methods to create, retrieve, delete, list, and persist applicants. Implements IUserRepo to provide generic user operations.
